quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,77,Kodi iwo sadziwa kuti Mulungu amadziwa zimene iwo amabisa ndi zimene amaziulula
  2,78,Ndipo pali ena mwa iwo amene ndi osaphunzira amene sadziwa za m’Buku koma amakhulupirira mabodza ndi zongoganizira chabe
  2,79,"Motero tsoka kwa iwo amene amalemba Buku ndi manja awo ndipo amanena kuti: “Mawu awa achoka kwa Mulungu ndi kugula ndi ilo mphatso yochepa”. Tsoka kwa iwo pa zimene alemba manja awo ndipo tsoka kwa iwo pa zimene akupeza chifukwa cha izo"
  2,80,"Iwo adati: “Ife sitidzakhudzidwa ndi moto kupatula masiku owerengeka okha”. Nena: “Kodi inu mwapanga lonjezo ndi Mulungu limene Iye sadzaphwanya? Kapena kodi inu mumanena zinthu zokhudzana Mulungu zimene simuzidziwa?”"
  2,81,"Inde! Yense amene achita zoipa ndipo azunguliridwa ndi machimo ake, adzakhala eni ake a Gahena. Kumeneko adzakhalako mpaka kalekale"
  2,82,"Ndipo iwo amene ali ndi chikhulupiriro ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino, iwo ndi eni ake a Paradiso ndipo adzakhala komweko mpaka kale kale"
  2,83,"Ndi pamene Ife tinamvana ndi ana a Israeli: “Musapembedze wina koma Mulungu yekha ndipo onetsani chifundo kwa makolo anu, kwa abale anu, kwa ana a masiye ndi kwa anthu ovutika, ndipo auzeni anthu kuti azichita zabwino. Pempherani pa nthawi yake ndipo perekani msonkho wothandizila anthu osauka”. Komatu inu mudabwerera m’mbuyo kupatula owerengeka okha ndipo simudalabadire china chilichonse"